The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.80% p.a.. The First Trust Emerging Markets AlphaDEX UCITS ETF Acc is the only ETF that tracks the Nasdaq AlphaDEX® Emerging Markets index. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by full replication (buying all the index constituents). The dividends in the ETF are accumulated and reinvested in the ETF. The First Trust Emerging Markets AlphaDEX UCITS ETF Acc is a very small ETF with 12m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 9 April 2013 and is domiciled in Ireland.
